This text file is in reference to Question 2
Question 2 contains 3 files

1. main.cpp -
	the main driver file
2. Polar.hpp
	Declarations regarding Polar class
3. Polar.cpp
	definitions of Polar Class
Read the corresponding file for explanations .

Compile using the command : g++ *.cpp -o question2
If this does not work I.e gives warning related to c++11 
Then try clang++ -std=c++11 -stdlib=libc++ *.cpp -o question2

Note - All The files compiled successfully and gave output in XCODE
